              </tr> 
              <tr> 
               <td><a href="http://www.iris.washington.edu/mailman/listinfo/webservices">Webservices</a> </td> 
               <td><span class="caps">IRIS</span> Web Services List</td> 
              </tr> 
             </tbody>
            </table> 
            <p><strong><span class="caps">DHI</span>/FISSURES Mailing Lists:</strong> There are two mailing lists which are relevant to <span class="caps">DHI</span>/FISSURES: <a href="http://www.iris.washington.edu/mailman/listinfo/dhi-clients">dhi-clients</a> and <a href="http://www.iris.washington.edu/mailman/listinfo/dhi-servers">dhi-servers</a>.</p> 
            <h2><span class="caps">IRIS</span> Bulkmail Service – Send announcements to the <span class="caps">IRIS</span> community</h2> 
            <p>The <span class="caps">IRIS</span> bulkmail service is available to those users who want to inform the <span class="caps">IRIS</span> community of related employment opportunities, workshops or other relevant announcements. The bulkmail submission will be reviewed by <span class="caps">IRIS</span> staff and you will be notified by email regarding the status of the request.</p> 
            <h3>Using <span class="caps">IRIS</span> Bulkmail</h3> 
            <p>To send an announcement to the <span class="caps">IRIS</span> community, please fill out the <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/about_iris/mailing_lists/bulkmail"><span class="caps">IRIS</span> Bulkmail Request Form</a>.</p> 
            <p>Bulkmail List subscribers can post a message to all the list members, by sending email to <a href="mailto:bulkmail@iris.washington.edu">bulkmail@iris.washington.edu</a></p> 
            <h3>Subscribing to <span class="caps">IRIS</span> Bulkmail</h3> 
            <p>You can subscribe to the list, or change your existing subscription, using the form on the <a href="http://www.iris.washington.edu/mailman/listinfo/bulkmail"><span class="caps">IRIS</span> Bulkmail Info Page</a>.</p> 
           </article> 
           <section> 
            <p class="text-center"><em> by <a href="/ds/newsletter/author/knight-tim/"> Tim Knight </a> (IRIS Data Management Center) </em></p> 
